        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-12 mt-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="text-orange-500 text-4xl">üßò</span>
            <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Flexibility</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <span class="text-orange-500 text-4xl">üåø</span>
